@host = http://localhost:3000
@baseUrl = {{host}}/api/v1
@token = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### SEARCH MODULE - Full-Text Search
### ============================================

### SEARCH - Global Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=keyword&page=1&limit=20&entities=contact,deal,document
Authorization: {{token}}

### SEARCH - Search by Entity
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/:entity?q=keyword&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: {{token}}

### Notes:
### - All endpoints require authentication
### - Searchable entities: contact, deal, activity, document, zettel
### - Replace UUIDs with actual IDs from your database
